      <title>高等级公司债券交易价格日益接近垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/high-grade-company-bonds-increasingly-trade-near-junk-levels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些购买垃圾债券的基金经理转而将资金投入投资级债券，因为现在的收益率几乎一样高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/high-grade-company-bonds-increasingly-trade-near-junk-levels</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
